{"tid":808091,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果當日韓信聽蒯徹講自立，三分天下，局勢會發展成點？","createTime":"2018-09-06T05:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T06:06:55.000Z","uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"46936dac3d6a4953694dfe5c968a3201ac207100","tid":808091,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"蒯徹：「參分天下，鼎足而居，其勢莫敢先動。夫以足下之賢聖，有甲兵之眾，據彊齊，從燕、趙，出空虛之地而製其後，因民之欲，西鄉為百姓請命，則天下風走而響應矣，孰敢不聽！」"},{"pid":"84d83143f6be6f0111edd8a5594c46e6dc855669","tid":808091,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:32:52.000Z","msg":"劉邦自己帶兵打彭城都打輸<br />\n夾埋其他諸侯打項羽三萬兵都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf0215868483722e88b55c60ff80f3d92f30246","tid":808091,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:04:46.000Z","msg":"食晒成個天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8124d8073fbb4d1cbb22f5f783734ac5ce7ecb25","tid":808091,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e34a80d04cd80065ea175fb8b3b012068cf33e6e","tid":808091,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98a644e3e9f77e643554d756d490d00a6fc5544","tid":808091,"uid":175108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"聽唔知邊位巴打講<br />\n劉邦將韓信嘅兵同將換晒做親信<br />\n冇乜可能反到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36e7683073e51f000ea3bee2dee6536b6b06a1f","tid":808091,"uid":139573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"早四百年入三國時代<br />\n不過韓信識帶兵<br />\n但治天下能力真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c00b2dac2b